  "description": "The hoodie isn't just something you throw on when it's cold. It's kind of like a superhero costume for real life. One piece of clothing, a million moods. It can make you feel cozy, invisible, bold, or protected. And whether you know it or not, every time someone puts one on, they're stepping into a story that started long before TikTok, iPads, or even the internet.",
